{"tid":1429001,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[航空]連登飛機膠討論區37","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:34:20.000Z","uid":6122,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"34b50d3212fa5ccfe08ef9dc09cb576a40ecdc84","tid":1429001,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#FreedomHK</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n上回討論 <br />\n[航空]連登飛機膠討論區36<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344300</a><br />\n<br />\n相關討論<br />\n777經濟艙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/56067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/56067</a><br />\n北衛星客運廊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/49598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/49598</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n呢個post將會有人不定時講返:<br />\n<del>ITM唔飛得/幾時可以飛四引擎</del>Trump G20 達成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHNA幾時執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHX幾時入聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCX幾時離開OW<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA380係時變真&middot;奴隸船<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n777X幾時黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOW下個邊個破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKE幾時又同DL鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坡佬777幾時轉3-4-3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南太平洋<del>幾時開得成</del><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收咗皮啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皇天擊殺海航董事長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nT2譚仔幾時搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nITM幾時開國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCX/HX/QR/CZ etc幾時出入轉Alliance<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個Mile/FFP值得玩/MR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCX/KA TPE飛機餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA380<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>已經</strong></span>停產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>UO幾時搬入因航城/龍屋</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">譚仔又飛啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://files.rei.idv.tw/thumb/older/f8d482cd828c312ff05368c24a1c8ca5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffiles.rei.idv.tw%2Fthumb%2Folder%2Ff8d482cd828c312ff05368c24a1c8ca5.jpg&h=4859e152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">腳圖自己貼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1ec7ec86694088f5efb078de5c6ceafa8ca965","tid":1429001,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d4131ee3ce9326c86e6d7125d704ce2e07a01c33","tid":1429001,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.sj33.cn/uploads/allimg/201401/7-140122010458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum